06:47.309 --> 07:12.844
uh there was conflict developing with the rest of the world, let's say Russia and China and whomever. In any event uh North Korea attacked South Korea in June 1950 and president Harry S Truman at the time ordered American forces in to the relief of South Korea. I want to stop you right there just a second because we're showing a picture. We referred to Bob Middleton who you referred to in your book.

